## Field guidance
- subject: the main subject/content of the image
- style: the artistic/visual style (e.g. photorealistic, watercolor, flat vector)
- composition: layout, framing, and viewpoint
- mood: the emotional tone/atmosphere
- palette: dominant colors or color scheme
- constraints: hard requirements or things to avoid (e.g. "no text", "square crop")
- notes_from_references: if reference images were attached, what to preserve or draw from them (style, subject, composition); otherwise null
- search_queries: 1-3 short web search queries that would help find similar or reference imagery for this request
